Frederick C. Lane and Joel J. Cohen were named co-heads of an expanded merger and acquisitions group of this merchant banking company.
They will focus primarily on transactions that don't require capital investment of the firm.
Mr. Lane, 40 years old, has been a Donaldson merger specialist, while Mr. Cohen, 51, was a senior partner at the New York law firm of Davis, Polk, & Wardwell. 

